metadata.name: Hot DeFi Summer
metadata.description: Summer 2022 is approaching. Everyone participating in the Hedera NFT & DeFi ecosystems is prepping their swimsuits, beach towels, and sun-drenched liquidity. To celebrate, we thought it appropriate to mint an ice cream NFT on Hedera and send it on a little road trip for summer vacation... to where you might ask? You'll find out soon enough.
metadata.creator: Hedera
